{"tid":1854592,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"而家知民主係好野嚟啦","createTime":"2020-01-31T14:35:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-31T15:16:50.000Z","uid":303364,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0c2885472ea1f46c5af3e3d4c48816f1e5a3a964","tid":1854592,"uid":303364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T14:35:44.000Z","msg":"有<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">民主</span></span><br />\n<br />\n一個<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔理香港人死活</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔封關</span></span><br />\n搞到你人心惶惶<br />\n唔知每日有幾多大陸友潛伏喺香港散播病毒<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">冇支援</span></span><br />\n搞到你要半夜三更 天寒地凍落街排隊<br />\n每日要費神上網睇<br />\n都唔知買唔買到啲好基本既衛生用品 口罩 搓手液<br />\n既<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">仆街</span></span>就唔會做到香港既首長<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一個<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無知白痴</span></span><br />\n同你講蒸口罩可以重用<br />\n既<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">人渣</span></span>就唔會做到香港既議員<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">民主</span></span><br />\n<br />\n香港人就可以自己選擇<br />\n一個<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">知道香港人既需要<br />\n會聆聽市民聲音</span></span><br />\n起碼<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">識忘羊補牢 實施適當既政策</span></span><br />\n既<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">正常人</span></span>做首長<br />\n<br />\n選擇一班<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">有良知<br />\n有常識</span></span>既好人做議員<br />\n<br />\n而家知我哋<br />\n點解要<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">祈求民主與自由萬世都不撓</span></span>啦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">藍絲</span>們 醒未啊<br />\n大家都要襯而家點醒身邊啲<span style=\"color: blue;\">人</span>啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">康復香港 時代抗疫<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 決一不可<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"a3f95b701cd566a6cf5070aceb4d37ffea3fdc64","tid":1854592,"uid":303364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T14:37:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f7aa0d7ca5408085e349351198cae9f83bcfc3bb","tid":1854592,"uid":303364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T14:38:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7fc9d783d627e7032251b02b0e6ebfeeb1408b4b","tid":1854592,"uid":303364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T14:38:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c16d1b52197e3e8ca45b0dfe9f08435c69b33ff0","tid":1854592,"uid":303364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T14:39:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8d2b6a3a38ba75f22467cc4c94a89201c67ee325","tid":1854592,"uid":303364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T14:39:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"97781539f2269b658049d3efed98ab8f45a6184c","tid":1854592,"uid":303364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T14:39:46.000Z","msg":"唔"},{"pid":"d02b2a47d6e170937c9a2253bc4b894376c4794e","tid":1854592,"uid":303364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T14:39:58.000Z","msg":"郁"},{"pid":"f612bc5c5cd444909acdfa165746ec0c9d120356","tid":1854592,"uid":149844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T14:40:05.000Z","msg":"今世好開心識到各位同路人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n下世會小心投胎"},{"pid":"ebf52856f19c8df38f5169195d874034fea5b471","tid":1854592,"uid":303364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f612bc5c5cd444909acdfa165746ec0c9d120356","tid":1854592,"uid":149844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T14:40:05.000Z","msg":"今世好開心識到各位同路人<img sr